description: Erection of new care/nursing home in a part 2, part 4 storey building providing Convent (24 rooms) and ancillary accommodation; 33 residential care rooms; 19 x 1 bed residential units (Class C2); Chapel and erection of three residential blocks (part 3, part 4 and part 5 storey blocks) to provide 83 residential units, comprising 47 x 1 bed, 9 x 2 bed, 23 x 3 bed and 4 x 4 bed units plus ground and basement level car parking. Demolition of existing care/nursing home.
